ry girl in London who helps the war effort by parachuting into German-occupied France to help kidnap an important German general. She bungles through to a heroic finish of plot and counter-plot.","genre_ids":[35,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7791,"vote_count":34,"poster_path":"/xQpq0EopAjrAmkeX7Bo3MCKRtz6.jpg","release_date":"1959-09-18","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/n4KbSGafzC9P2e8piNf8E3eKqb6.jpg","original_title":"Babette s'en va-t-en guerre","original_language":"fr"},{"id":575848,"adult":false,"title":"Berlin Bouncer","video":false,"overview":"A portrait of Berlin’s most famous bouncers – Sven Marquardt, Frank Künster and Smiley Baldwin. The three men have been part and parcel of the capital’s club scene for more than 25 years – from the days after the fall of the Berlin Wall to the present day – but aren’t yet considering calling it a day even though life makes more demands on them as they turn 50.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3934,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/woBlfYZdP4BnQspcU5HzktFlipD.jpg","release_date":"2019-04-11","vote_average":6.262,"backdrop_path":"/mdOCf920Kjztc1mPdFfzhuSHBw1.jpg","original_title":"Berlin Bouncer","original_language":"de"},{"id":364664,"adult":false,"title":"Lazy Hazy Crazy","video":false,"overview":"Childhood friends Tracy, Chloe and Alice share an apartment over the summer. They live close together, meet guys and sell their company as well as sex.  With a romantic imagery and sometimes provocative theme the female debutant director Luk Yee-sum give the audience a playful story about sexuality, desire and friendship.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4021,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/f52gazV0PJmIEJTTYkYeHNKjlfm.jpg","release_date":"2015-10-29","vote_average":4.667,"backdrop_path":"/uB2OahNqNWjbIBFXq76FJjXFMMR.jpg","original_title":"同班同學","original_language":"cn"},{"id":542781,"adult":false,"title":"Killer Kate!","video":false,"overview":"Kate attends her est